Description: Device for representing an Arduino Due board with a footprint in an EAGLE design. Created by Dave Young for Element14. More EAGLE documentation at: http://www.element14.com/community/community/knode/cadsoft_eagle

Parts: 1.8VA, 1.8VD, 3V3, CLK, GND, IOUT+, IOUT-, SCLK, SDIO, SDO, TP5, VIN_NEG, VIN_POS
